</nav></header><main aria-label="main content"><div class="speakable">
      <b data-is-speakable>Ahead Of Trump-Kim Summit, Here's Where The U.S. Stands On North Korea</b>   <b data-is-speakable>President Trump hopes to make progress in his meeting with North Korea's Kim Jong Un this week, but he has resisted pressure to set firm timelines for the regime to give up its nuclear weapons.</b>
</div>
